Hello,

I have a container "cabinet" with these attributes:
```
	openMsg:function() {
		msg("Creeeeaaaakkkkk")
	},
	closeMsg:function() {
		msg("Groooaaaannnn")
	},
```
openMsg works as expected and replaces the default response.
but closeMsg does not. it shows the default close message.
